  "detailed_description": "\"NAGAISAN\" is an adventure game based on urban legends.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187770/extras/0e664ea2c3d4b5657b62b7cc01c6dc8f.avif?t=1768175662\" width=616 height=158 /></span><br><br>◆ Story<br><br>I came to know \"her\". Since then, I've felt someone's gaze from somewhere.<br><br>Memories of a place reached while searching for a lost dog in the past. I'm not sure if it's related, but I did something.<br><br>\"NAGAISAN\" can come from anywhere.<br><br>Even in dreams...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3187770/extras/325c1d1aae0ae0df8798e53ec09a8d09.avif?t=1768175662\" width=616 height=158 /></span><br><br>◆ Game Features<br><br>    Walking simulator where various events occur as you walk.<br>    Progress the story by examining objects.<br>    No quest markers or time limits, allowing for relaxed gameplay.<br>    \"NAGAISAN\" likes you.<br><br>Playtime: 15 minutes to 40 minutes.<br><br>◆ Streaming Guidelines<br><br>    Streaming is allowed without permission for both individuals and businesses.",
